00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:40,950
[Footprints of Change]

2
00:01:50,229 --> 00:01:52,780
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:58,920
For the past 10 years, all my efforts

4
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,400
have focused on changing

5
00:02:01,509 --> 00:02:04,170
the public's prejudice
against our Zeng family

6
00:02:04,710 --> 00:02:05,870
so that eventually

7
00:02:06,710 --> 00:02:08,280
we can enter politics and business

8
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,140
with an image of loving the people

9
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:12,040
and obeying the law.

10
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,400
Therefore,

11
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:17,020
public opinion is extremely important.

12
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,800
That wretched son of mine, Dalun,

13
00:02:18,889 --> 00:02:25,410
[Prosperity Through Virtue]

14
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:22,750
has struck
the public's most sensitive nerve

15
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,630
at the worst possible moment.

16
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,100
"Of all evils, lust is the worst."

17
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,430
And the victim happened to be

18
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:32,160
a young girl from a poor family.

19
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:37,079
Naturally, this has provoked
public outrage and widespread anger.

20
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:42,910
What do you think?

21
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:44,900
Father, you're right.

22
00:02:47,910 --> 00:02:48,470
But...

23
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,030
Dalun is your only son.

24
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:57,430
Throughout history, there have been many
who betrayed their parents.

25
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:58,690
I can't control him...

26
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,030
so let the law handle him.

27
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,710
Master,
Young Master Zeng has been arrested.

28
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:08,750
So be it.

29
00:03:13,130 --> 00:03:13,780
Father,

30
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,080
the court hasn't convicted him yet.

31
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,510
We can still bail him out.

32
00:03:23,790 --> 00:03:24,340
Father,

33
00:03:25,210 --> 00:03:25,940
I'll go then.

34
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:32,800
Ao.

35
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,590
Bring some fine tea

36
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,620
to Detective Wang.

37
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:42,240
Okay.

38
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:44,900
Take some fine tea

39
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:45,960
and call Cheng over.

40
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,020
Yes, Young Master.

41
